<h3 class="date"><a href="/2006/oct/16/">&#x27a0;</a> October 16, 2006</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="qa_jobs_on_ipod" >

        
        <a name="003004"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://msnbc.msn.com/id/15262121/site/newsweek/page/3/">Q&amp;A: Jobs on iPod&#39;s Cultural Impact - Newsweek</a></h4>

        

        <p>Steve Jobs: &#8220;I&#8217;ve seen the demonstrations on the Internet about how you can find another person using a Zune and give them a song they can play three times. It takes forever. By the time you&#8217;ve gone through all that, the girl&#8217;s got up and left! You&#8217;re much better off to take one of your earbuds out and put it in her ear. Then you&#8217;re connected with about two feet of headphone cable.&#8221;.  Subtle subtext:  &#8220;iPods get you laid&#8221;</p>

