    <div class="well" id="gigaom_dvd_jon" >

        
        <a name="002966"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://featured.gigaom.com/2006/10/02/dvd-jon-fairplays-apple/">GigaOM » DVD Jon Fairplays Apple</a></h4>

        

        <p>Could be interesting &#8212; DVDJon reverse engineered Apple&#8217;s DRM, and is looking to license it to other companies wanting to sell DRMed tracks.  Of course, Apple can break it again with a firmware update, so who knows where this is going.</p>

